text:
[[Lightkeeper|lightkeeper]] Dolarashynach is the Eternal Flame of the [[Light of Siberys]] in [[Argonnessen]]. She guides the Soldiers of the Light from [[Verthicha'vivex]],
the Mountain of Victory.
title: Dolarashynach
